                        <interp inst="t18390812-name-193" type="given" value="BENJAMIN"></interp>BENJAMIN ROBERTS</persName>
                  </hi>.(<hi rend="italic">police-constable G</hi> 22.) I stopped the prisoner in White's-court, about five o'clock in the morning of the 6th of August, and asked him what he had in his bundle—he refused to tell me—I said he must go with me to where he brought it from—he refused—I took him to the station-house, and found it was these things.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
